These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: pink, orange, fuchsia, ebony, apricot, brown
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, tennis, biathlon, skateboarding, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 2. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 3. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
 4. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
 5. the person who likes brown is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who likes brown##7
 7. the person who likes pink is not to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##8
 8. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who's sport is sailing##3
 9. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
10. the person who's sport is climbing is not to the left of the person who likes ebony##8
11. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
12. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes ebony##1
13. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##5
14. the person who likes brown is somewhere between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who likes fuchsia##7
15. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is climbing##5
16. the person who likes apricot is not the person who's sport is biathlon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Color           | ebony | orange | pink | apricot | brown | fuchsia |
| Sport   | climbing | tennis    | sailing  | skateboarding  | biathlon            | rugby  |

