.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, havana, pall-mall, oliveros, davidoff, dannemann
The people use 6 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat, bus, helicopter, bike, skateboard
 1. the oliveros-smoker is not the person driving the skateboard##6
 2. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
 3. the person driving the bike is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person driving the skateboard is between the oliveros-smoker and the person driving the boat##2
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bus##5
 7. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the pall-mall-smoker##5
 8. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 9. the havana-smoker is not the person driving the helicopter##6
10. the bolivar-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
11. the davidoff-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
12. the person driving the skateboard is not to the right of the davidoff-smoker##8
13. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
14. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
15. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | dannemann | havana | davidoff | oliveros | bolivar |
| Transport     | bus  | snowmobile  | boat         | skateboard | bike    | helicopter   |

