 9. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of soul##5
10. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the van is somewhere between the fan of techno and the person driving the car##7
12. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
13. the fan of hip-hop is between the person driving the bike and the person driving the van##2
14. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
15. the person driving the car is somewhere between the person driving the van and the fan of reggae##7
16. the person driving the bike is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8
17. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
