 3. the person who growszinnia is between the owner of the bird and the person who growsmarigold##2
 4. the person who growsbellflower is in an even position##4
 5. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the owner of the snake##7
 6. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
 7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
 9. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
10. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
12. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the person who growszinnia##7
13. the owner of the pony is not to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##8
14. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
15. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
16. the person who growsbegonia is in an even position##4
