The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, rock-climbing, baking, board-games, woodworking, filmmaking
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's birthday is in september##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in july##2
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
 9. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
10. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
12. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is chess##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |   3    |     4      |     5     |    6     |
| Birthday   | september | november | july  | june     | march | may |
| Hobby           | chess        | baking    | filmmaking | rock-climbing | woodworking     | board-games  |

