.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-18::.
6 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, guinea-pig, frog, rabbit, hedgehog
There are 6 different nationalities: thai, egyptian, nigerian, australian, mexican, indian
 1. the mexican is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
 2. the mexican is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the egyptian##7
 3. the mexican is not the owner of the rabbit##6
 4. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
 5. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
 6. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the indian##8
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 9. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
10. the egyptian is somewhere to the right of the thai##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
12. the thai is not to the right of the mexican##8
13. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
14. the thai is not to the left of the owner of the rabbit##8
15. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
16. the thai is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
17. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |   3    |  4   |      5      |   6    |
