.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-19::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  entrepreneur, analyst, manager, designer, dancer, scientist
6 different games are played: chess, domino, backgammon, snooker, bridge, whist
 1. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5
 2. the person playing chess is not to the left of the entrepreneur##8
 3. the analyst is the analyst##1
 4. the designer is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the scientist is on the right of the manager##1
 6. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
 7. the entrepreneur is not the person playing bridge##6
 8. the analyst is not to the left of the person playing domino##8
 9. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the right of the person playing domino##5
10. the person playing snooker is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
11. the person playing whist is on the right of the dancer##1
12. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the entrepreneur##8
13. the person playing backgammon is not to the right of the person playing chess##8
14. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the designer##8
15. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the scientist##5
16. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
17. the scientist is not to the left of the dancer##8
18. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the designer##5
19. the analyst is not to the right of the person playing backgammon##8

.:: Answer ::.
