 1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
 2. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##8
 3. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
 4. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
 5. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person who likes green##8
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not the person who likes orange##6
 9. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
10. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
11. the person who likes blood-red is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4
13. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the person who likes mauve##5
14. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
15. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is singing##5
16. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes blood-red##1
17. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes orange##5
18. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who likes blue##5
19. the person who likes blue is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
20. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
21. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who likes orange##8

.:: Answer ::.
